snippet.title: Out and About: Kickstarter Trailer (2023)
snippet.description:
This is an outdated trailer, check our channel for the newest, much improved trailers! :)

Out and About is a cozy life simulator about foraging, community and food. Explore nature, identify and gather plants & fungi, cook recipes and herbal remedies and sell them on the farmers market - all while bringing the community together and turning a damaged coastal town into a foodie paradise.
